## Infographic Overview
- The image is an informational graphic titled "DETOX YOUR BODY" (2 of 2 claude). The website www.herbs-info.com is displayed at the top (1 of 2 claude) or top right corner (1 of 2 claude).
- It shows a silhouette or outline of a human torso (2 of 2 claude), divided into six colored sections, each representing a different bodily system or organ (2 of 2 claude).
- Each section lists foods that allegedly or supposedly support or help detoxification of that specific system or area (2 of 2 claude).
- Overall, the graphic appears to suggest or show specific foods that supposedly or might help or support detoxification of different or specific organs and systems, presented in a visually organized manner (2 of 2 claude).
- Unique Claim: Contact information "info@nutritionsolutionlifestyle.com" is shown at the bottom of the image (1 of 2 claude).

## Bodily Systems and Associated Foods
- **BLOOD**
    - Color: Represented by a salmon/orange (1 of 2 claude) or salmon/pink (1 of 2 claude) section.
    - Foods: Lists Cayenne Pepper, Red Grapes, Wheatgrass, Moringa, Garlic, Leafy Greens, Kale, Beans, Oregano, and Coconut Water (2 of 2 claude).
- **LYMPH**
    - Color: Represented by a blue/teal (1 of 2 claude) or light blue (1 of 2 claude) section.
    - Foods: Includes Sea Vegetables, Asparagus, Carrots, Guava, Lettuce, Strawberries, Lemon Water, and Fruits & Vegetable Juices (2 of 2 claude).
- **LIVER**
    - Color: Represented by a green section (2 of 2 claude).
    - Foods: Features Bitter Gourd, Leafy Greens, Grapefruit, Barley Grass, Avocado, Lemon, Spinach, Walnuts, Apples, Dandelion Greens, Garlic, and Arugula (2 of 2 claude).
- **GALLBLADDER**
    - Color: Represented by a light orange (1 of 2 claude) or tan (1 of 2 claude) section.
    - Foods: Lists Cucumber, Lentils, Tomatoes, Watermelon, Beans, Avocado, Whole Grains, Beets, Legumes, Garlic & Onion, Okra, and Sweet Potato (2 of 2 claude).
- **PANCREAS**
    - Color: Represented by a gray section (2 of 2 claude).
    - Foods: Includes Spinach, Cabbage, Cherries, Broccoli, Red Reishi Mushroom, Sweet Potatoes, and Blueberries (2 of 2 claude).
- **KIDNEYS**
    - Color: Represented by a yellow/gold (1 of 2 claude) or gold/yellow (1 of 2 claude) section.
    - Foods: Contains Cranberries, Turmeric, Red Bell Pepper, Cabbage, Raspberries, and Olive Oil (2 of 2 claude).
- **INTESTINES**
    - Color: Represented by a pink section (2 of 2 claude).
    - Foods: Lists Tomatoes, Flax Seed, Pineapple, Cauliflower, Cherimoya, Artichokes, Onion, Eggplant, Dragonfruit, Papaya, Chili Pepper, and Lentils (2 of 2 claude).
